data.text:
Boys and Girls in 7th and 8th grade are able to participate in track at Webster. Webster girls have a 7th and an 8th grade team and boys have a 7th and an 8th grade team. The season runs from the beginning of April to late May. All boys and girls that go out for track will have the opportunity to participate.

Webster won the boys conference championships and conference relays 6 of the last 8 seasons! Girls won the conference championships 5 of the last 8 seasons!
